hen I asked you, you lied to me. It means YOU ARE DISHONEST.LOVE and AFFECTION are two essential elements of HUMAN RELATIONSHIP. However, whether you deserve my LOVE and AFFECTION or not is based on your TRUSTWORTHINESS and HONESTY.', 12638, 0), (179296, 'Sometimes the most difficult relationships to get over are the ones that never were.', 33019, 0), (179297, 'Fell in love first,Fell in love quickly—Like I was pushed.Fell in love next,Fell in love slowly—Like I was strolling.Falling in love now And feeling crazy.Thinking of closing my eyesAnd jumping.', 3588, 0), (179298, 'Many marriages would have been laid to rest a long time ago, if they were not on a life-support machine called other people’s opinions and/or expectations.', 4616, 0), (179299, 'People always give higher priority to newer one, whatever it is.. Relation or thing.', 12274, 0), (179300, 'I Am The Way, The Truth and The Life; no one comes to The Father but by Me', 17018, 0);
